{"type": "article", "id": 30507, "title": "这个设计工作室，总是能让司空见惯的东西自己讲故事", "description": "他们的设计主题是“想要在空间和物体之间创造新的故事”。", "date": "2016-08-05T23:36:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 920, "name": "家居设计"}], "category": 17, "author": 329238, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 326, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160803131916m6D0xecU5sbjwRAP.jpg", "contents": "<p><a href=\"http://yoy-idea.jp/works/\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本 YOY 设计工作室</a>最近和<a href=\"http://www.mitsuichemicals.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">三井化学（Mitsui Chemicals ）</a>合作了这款中空的靠垫，名为“花边” （Lace）。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803132127Ewv9RL1TuNaxcrCi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657576\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Lace</p></figcaption></figure></div><p>这个看起来是手工制作的靠垫，实际上是由坚固又轻盈的的弹性聚氨酯制成。有了三井化学的技术支持，设计师们成功让这款靠垫的舒适度和传统靠垫一样。Lace 目前只有样品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803132450BfeMyWNlHVQXPj60.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">按压之后不会变形，看上去也清爽</p></figcaption></figure></div><p>YOY 工作室是由空间设计师 Naoki Ono 和产品设计师 Yuki Yamamoto 一起成立的。他们的设计主题是“想要在空间和物体之间创造新的故事”。</p><p>两人还在今年的 NYC x DESIGN 纽约设计周大奖中得了智能设计奖的创新奖（ Design Intelligence Award / Innovation Prize）。</p><p>在今年的米兰设计周上，他们带去了这款椅子 CUTOUT ：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803132917wj62Puv5G3ZXgW9x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333871\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">CUTOUT</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803132843zJ7koUIXsN1EV9b4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333871\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803132851oxNHhMcr0CdIPEvi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333871\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803132831ZzATDWftdXxuKFYl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333871\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>CUTOUT 椅背中空的部分好像是被取下来用作了椅子的座位和前脚。</p><p>这款叫 BLOW 的架子也能作为家里的一个小惊喜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803133503tSbL0eaMgElo3wRs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667262\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">BLOW</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803133737ONeT1kPaKHxWslJ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608031337502h9rnJepNyKHkZxF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667262\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803133620QLavPV9sdwgSl8yf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667262\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>这些架子单看好像是被风吹散的纸张，其实它们是用 A4 大小的薄铁片制成的。有 5 种不同的形状，它们很容易可以固定在墙上。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803134459MRlD6oY5AjgVBqNJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIGHT</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">LIGHT 是极富原创性的灯，只有两部分构成：支柱和电线。顶部有一个内置的 LED 光源，是一个灯罩的形状，当 LED 发亮时，墙上就会投射出灯罩的形状，光亮的强度跟一个标准的台灯相当。LIGHT 有两种样式：床头灯和落地灯。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803134716ixs0H1NgqfT4kY2y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\" style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803134759bYvg7LUth9q3xRH1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\" style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608031347297GP6N0cAp3Do8O5U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Poster 也有异曲同工之妙。它用了 A2 规格的一张纸，有一些小的切口，就形成了一个简单的灯罩。只要用胶带或者图钉就可以把它挂到墙上了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803135612TBUcS8m5PCzF1eHE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666129\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803135537WfV0gX48nusoebZD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666129\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803135551Ue3ShdR2usCvFKj9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666129\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803135510ECesnMbSdfLoVNjt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666129\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure>\r\n  \r\n</div><p class=\"\">文内图及题图来源：<a href=\"http://yoy-idea.jp/works/\" rel=\"nofollow\">YOY 官网</a>、<a href=\"http://www.journal-du-design.fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">journaldudesign</a></p>"}